<br>
Ice is frozen water.  Water is anathema to fire.  Therefore, a fire ELEMENTAL pet should not cast ice spells.<br>
<br>
A water pet can cast ice spells all it wants.  Ice is frozen water, after all.  That makes sense.  But they shouldn't be very strong, as the water pet is modeled after the rogue.<br>
<br>
Let's get this perfectly straight right here and now.<br>
<br>
Wizards ARE NOT against having a fire pet that is worth using.<br>
<br>
We ARE against our class-defining spells being used by pets, which, in the grand scheme of things, are backup party members.<br>
<br>
Ice Comet, though only leverl 49, <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>is</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> a wizard class-defining spell.  In pre-Kunark EQ, it was <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>the</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> spell to get.  It was the epitome of wizard spells.  And until 60, there is no other spell that matches its damage.<br>
<br>
Give fire pets spells that make sense, up their melee output and leave the ice spells for someone else. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showMessageRange?topicID=165.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showMessageRange?topicID=165.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showMessageRange?topicID=165.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showMessageRange?topicID=165.topic&start=81&stop=82>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showPrevMessage?topicID=165.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showNextMessage?topicID=165.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=165.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.threadControl?topicID=165.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=165.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm44.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=165.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Cli